g-speech-al-qawl"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-8EE","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":36744,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/08\/01\/dead-among-living\/","url_meta":{"origin":33272,"position":0},"title":"Hudhayfah on Fitnah: Who are the dead among the living?","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 1, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu al-Tufayl reported: It was said to Hudhayfah, may Allah be pleased with him, \u201cWho are the dead among the living?\u201d Hudhayfah said, \u201cThose who do not recognize good in their hearts and do not reject evil in their hearts.\u201d Source: Mus\u0323annaf Ibn Abi\u0304 Shaybah 37577 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0627\u0644\u0637\u0651\u064f\u0641\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0644\u0650 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34570,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/11\/29\/hudhayfah-fitnah-worst\/","url_meta":{"origin":33272,"position":1},"title":"Hudhayfah on Fitnah: Worst tribulation to not know good or evil","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 29, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"\u2018Amir reported: Hudhayfah, may Allah be pleased with him, was asked, \u201cWhich trial is the worst?\u201d Hudhayfah said, \u201cIt is when good and evil are before you and you do not know which of them to follow.\u201d Source: Mus\u0323annaf Ibn Abi\u0304 Shaybah 37569 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0627\u0645\u0650\u0631\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0633\u064f\u0626\u0650\u0644\u064e \u062d\u064f\u0630\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0641\u064e\u0629\u064f \u0631\u0636\u064a \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":35233,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/02\/15\/hudhayfah-nifaq-lightly\/","url_meta":{"origin":33272,"position":2},"title":"Hudhayfah on Nifaq: Beware of taking hypocrisy too lightly","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 15, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu al-Ruqad reported: Hudhayfah said, \u201cA man used to speak a word in the time of the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, by which he would become a hypocrite. Indeed, I hear one of you say it now in your gatherings ten times a day!\u201d Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32768,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/07\/12\/islam-vanishes-end-of-time\/","url_meta":{"origin":33272,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Islam: Disappearance of religious knowledge at end of time","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 12, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Hudhayfah ibn al-Yaman reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cIslam will be taken apart just as a garment is taken apart, until fasting is not known, nor prayer, nor rites, nor charity. The Book of Allah Almighty will vanish in a single night, such\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25068,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/07\/12\/fitnah-no-imam-withdraw-sects\/","url_meta":{"origin":33272,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Fitnah: If no Muslim leader, withdraw from all sects","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 12, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Hudhayfah ibn al-Yaman reported: The people used to ask the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, about good, but I would ask him about evil for fear it would overtake me. I said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, we were in ignorance and evil, but then Allah sent\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":38787,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/02\/15\/speak-evil-dead\/","url_meta":{"origin":33272,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Death: Do not speak evil about the deceased","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 15, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhen your companion dies, leave him alone and do not malign him.\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 4899 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Arna\u2019ut \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0627\u0626\u0650\u0634\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u062a\u0652 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633